$ VBA Module 00_ModuleLoader [Common]

The following module allows to load → development/languages/VBA/language/module[VBA modules] and → development/languages/VBA/language/classes[classes] programmatically.

code {
Sub load()

    call loadOrReplaceModuleWithFile("prog"  , "p:\rojects\main.bas")
    call loadOrReplaceModuleWithFile("person", "p:\rojects\person.cls", vbext_ct_ClassModule)
    
end sub
code }


gh|VBAModules|/Common/00_ModuleLoader.bas||

sa:

  → development/languages/VBA/modules/Common
